<item>
            <title>[LU-149] Lustre 1.8.x known issues tracking</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-149</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;While testing against Lustre b1_8 branch, we would hit known bugs which were already reported in Lustre Bugzilla. In order to move away from relying on Bugzilla, we would create a JIRA equivalent when we hit the known bug. This tracker ticket is a reference for all of the known bugs on b1_8 branch detected during the past daily/build/release testing cycles since Lustre 1.8.4 Build 01 (created on 2010-05-21).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="10482">LU-149</key>
            <summary>Lustre 1.8.x known issues tracking</summary>
