                            <comment id="11449" author="yujian" created="Mon, 28 Mar 2011 19:43:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The known issues has been tracked in the wiki page. Let&apos;s close this ticket.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="11276" author="yujian" created="Mon, 21 Mar 2011 21:10:18 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;I suggest it would be better to do this as a wiki page since so everyone could edit it to add jira issue links when they are created.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Done. Please refer to &lt;a href=&quot;http://wiki.whamcloud.com/display/ENG/Test+Trackers&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://wiki.whamcloud.com/display/ENG/Test+Trackers&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="11264" author="rread" created="Mon, 21 Mar 2011 08:44:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I suggest it would be better to do this as a wiki page since so everyone could edit it to add jira issue links when they are created.&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="11260" author="yujian" created="Mon, 21 Mar 2011 04:58:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Tracking date: 2011-03-22&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;lnet-selftest:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=21945&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 21945&lt;/a&gt; lnet-selftest.sh: FAIL: test_smoke lst Error found&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=23462&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 23462&lt;/a&gt; lnet-selftest: lst Error found&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;sgpdd-survey:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=23988&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 23988&lt;/a&gt; kernel BUG at drivers/scsi/sd.c&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;obdfilter-survey:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=23706&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 23706&lt;/a&gt; sles11sp1: jbd2 stat patch is missing&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=23979&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 23979&lt;/a&gt; ext4: obdfilter-survey async journal test_1b test_2b failed&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=23529&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 23529&lt;/a&gt; lustre client goes OOM w/ async journal commit enabled&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;sanity:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=22378&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 22378&lt;/a&gt; Correct MDS client stats&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=20569&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 20569&lt;/a&gt; sanity test_170: @@@@@@ FAIL: expected 517 bad lines, but got 518&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=21465&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 21465&lt;/a&gt; sanity test 27p: append to a truncated file with some full OSTs&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;sanity-benchmark:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=24072&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 24072&lt;/a&gt; sanity-benchmark: dbench failed (the client was evicted by mds)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;sanityn:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=18169&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 18169&lt;/a&gt; sanityN.sh test_4 failed (mismatched client/server clocks?)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;racer:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=15962&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 15962&lt;/a&gt; LustreError: 14169:0:(namei.c:773:ll_create_node()) ASSERTION(list_empty(&amp;amp;inode-&amp;gt;i_dentry)) failed&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=22690&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 22690&lt;/a&gt; BUG: unable to handle kernel paging request at virtual address 1d400178&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=16779&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 16779&lt;/a&gt; Racer (handler.c:927:mds_getattr_lock()) Can&apos;t unpack name&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;replay-single:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=23878&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 23878&lt;/a&gt; replay-single test_16: @@@@@@ FAIL: test_16 failed with 2 &lt;font color=&quot;red&quot;&gt;(1.8.6 blocker)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=23784&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 23784&lt;/a&gt; replay-single: several tests failed with Input/output error&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=24118&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 24118&lt;/a&gt; replay-single.sh: FAIL: test_70b rundbench load on sfire19 failed!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;replay-single, replay-vbr:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=23465&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 23465&lt;/a&gt; ll_statfs_internal()) mdc_statfs fails: rc = -108&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;recovery-small:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=21893&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 21893&lt;/a&gt; recovery-small test_59: @@@@@@ FAIL: read dd: reading `/mnt/lustre/f59&apos;: Input/output error 0 blocks, must be 1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;replay-ost-single:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=24431&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 24431&lt;/a&gt; replay-ost-single: test_5 iozone hangs &lt;font color=&quot;red&quot;&gt;(1.8.6 blocker)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;conf-sanity:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=23137&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 23137&lt;/a&gt; BUG: soft lockup - CPU#1 stuck for 10s! [kiblnd_sd_03:8135]&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=22300&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 22300&lt;/a&gt; conf_sanity test 47: mkfs.lustre FATAL: mkfs failed 256&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=23347&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 23347&lt;/a&gt; BUG: soft lockup - CPU#1 stuck for 10s! [automount:10284]&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=19526&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 19526&lt;/a&gt; conf-sanity test_46a: stat: cannot stat `/mnt/lustre/widestripe&apos;: Cannot send after transport endpoint shutdown&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=24101&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 24101&lt;/a&gt; conf-sanity test_45 causing client reboot&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=24472&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 24472&lt;/a&gt; general protection fault: 0000 [#1] SMP: RIP: class_del_profile+0x63/0x510 [obdclass] &lt;font color=&quot;red&quot;&gt;(1.8.6 blocker)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;performance-sanity:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=22564&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 22564&lt;/a&gt; performance_sanity test is timed out after running for 15000 seconds&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=23206&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 23206&lt;/a&gt; performance-sanity test_8: @@@@@@ FAIL: test_8 failed with 1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;sanity-quota:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=23470&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 23470&lt;/a&gt; quota_save_version defect: need to wait conf_param update&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=23720&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 23720&lt;/a&gt; sles11 sp1: sanity-quota: Portals memory leaked: 3152 bytes&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;parallel-scale:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=23935&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 23935&lt;/a&gt; parallel-scale test_write_append_truncate: trunc-after-APPEND bad [256193-289780]/[0x3e8c1-0x46bf4] != c &lt;font color=&quot;red&quot;&gt;(1.8.6 blocker)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;parallel-scale-nfsv4:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=22040&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 22040&lt;/a&gt; parallel_scale_nfsv4 test is timed out after running for 13000 seconds&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=22307&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 22307&lt;/a&gt; Console flooded with error message from ll_inode_from_lock() during NFS tests&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;recovery-mds-scale:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=23641&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 23641&lt;/a&gt; recovery-mds-scale FLAVOR=MDS: lustre-MDT0000: clients were evicted due to a lock blocking callback&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=22777&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 22777&lt;/a&gt; recovery-mds-scale FLAVOR=OSS: orphan recovery happens too late, causing writes to fail with ENOENT after recovery&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;mmp, recovery-mds-scale, recovery-double-scale, recovery-random-scale:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=20997&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 20997&lt;/a&gt; ll_fill_super()) Unable to process log: -108&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Other bugs:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=24303&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 24303&lt;/a&gt; kernel BUG at fs/inode.c:323! &lt;font color=&quot;red&quot;&gt;(1.8.6 blocker)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=24423&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 24423&lt;/a&gt; ost hangs, e2fsck doesn&apos;t find anything wrong &lt;font color=&quot;red&quot;&gt;(1.8.6 blocker)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=24437&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Bug 24437&lt;/a&gt; Issues with executable files on NFS share &lt;font color=&quot;red&quot;&gt;(1.8.6 blocker)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
